<Author>traveler70Apeldoorn
<Content>Friendly people and good service November 2008.We had booked another hotel but there were some problems so after some phonecalls we checked in at the BB hotel Berlin.The personel was very friendly and we've got a room directly.It was no problem that we were there very early (we left home, the Netherlands at 03.00 am so we were very tiered) In the morning they have a breakfast buffet with lots of different kind off food and in the evening the have diner. First you get a homemade soop, than diner and after that desert. It was realy tastefull.Our room was not so big, but it was clean and the bed's slept very well. The hotel was very close to the underground station and busses.We had a perfect stay in Berlin thanks to the personel of the BB Hotel. 
